That scale on the left is
not an insignificant number.

00:29:00.800 --> 00:29:02.070
But there was no growth.

00:29:02.230 --> 00:29:05.140
And at the orange star,
they localized into Chinese.

00:29:05.200 --> 00:29:06.250
And look what happened.

